&lt;p&gt;This Special Issue presents recent scientific and engineering contributions of research on the efficiency of energy sourcing, conversion and use, cleaner fuels and biofuels, cleaner production, GHG mitigation and reduction, process optimisation and waste management. The provided topical coverage reflects the breadth of the research presented at the PRES’23 conference, upgraded with follow-up research by the authors and thorough selection by the Guest Editors.&lt;/p&gt;
