&lt;p&gt;Carbon neutrality is a common development goal worldwide. To achieve this goal, promoting the conversion of wastes into resource or energy in construction and building up a circular construction serve as important measures. In view of this, this joint special issue aims to provide a platform to share and discuss the novel ideas, technologies, and research findings to promote interdisciplinary research on innovative valorization of alternative materials and waste towards circular construction.&lt;/p&gt;
