&lt;p&gt;This special issue will cover wide spectra of contributions that discusses role of digitalization with particular focus on the energy field with mandatory discussion of sustainability approaches. The digitalization made various technological solutions that are especially crucial and valuable in field of energy. On the other side sustainability aspect is key one to be able to understand long term implications to the environment of the emerging advanced solutions based on the information technologies. All these issues are assumed to be tackled within the herein proposed VSI. Practical and useful innovations in various engineering disciplines would be discussed within this VSI. All accepted contributions must have strong research background related to the focus of Clean Production and Sustainability in general. The VSI is to gather high quality submissions that would help to get insights and bridge current issues towards creation of the sustainable development visions of smart technologies in the energy digitalization era. Presented knowledge would be useful for academia members, industry professionals and policy makers.&lt;/p&gt;
