&lt;p&gt;You are invited to submit your manuscript at any time before the submission deadline. For any inquiries about the appropriateness of contribution topics, please contact Managing Guest Editor Prof Becky P.Y. Loo via bpyloo@hku.hk.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The journal’s submission platform &lt;a href="https://www.editorialmanager.com/SCSI"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Editorial Manager&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt;® is now available for receiving submissions to this Special Issue.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Please refer to the Guide for Authors to prepare your manuscript, and select the Article Type of &lt;strong&gt;“VSI: Peo-Env-Inf”&lt;/strong&gt; when submitting your manuscript online. Both the Guide for Authors and the submission portal could be found on the Journal Homepage here: &lt;a href="https://www.sciencedirect.com/journal/sustainable-cities-and-society"&gt;https://www.sciencedirect.com/journal/sustainable-cities-and-society&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;All the submissions deemed suitable to be sent for peer review will be reviewed by at least two independent reviewers. Upon its editorial acceptance, your article will go into production immediately. It will be published in the latest regular issue, while be presented on the specific Special Issue webpage simultaneously. In regular issues, Special Issue articles will be clearly marked and branded.&lt;/p&gt;
